articles.author: The Associated Press
articles.title: 2 fans die and an officer is in a coma after Champions League celebrations in France - NBC News
articles.description: PARIS — Two fans died and a police officer is in a coma after mass nationwide celebrations for Paris Saint-Germain's historic Champions League victory, European soccer's biggest prize, French authorities said Sunday.
